# RCV NOC Portal — module gateway routes.
#
# The Portal deployer writes one `<module>.caddy` snippet here when a module is
# installed and removes it on uninstall (issue #55, Gap 4), then reloads Caddy.
# This placeholder keeps the `import /etc/caddy/modules/*.caddy` glob in the
# Caddyfile matching at least one file before any module is deployed. It
# contains no directives, so it has no effect on routing. Do not delete.
